author: alex
msg: Moved mod_jk and mod_jserv source into new src/native/mod_jk and src/native/mod_jserv directories
Please be sure to do "cvs update -P" (or, better, "cvs update -fdRP") to make sure you have all and only the new directories/files
I have tested this for Linux and Apache 1.3; I'd really appreciate it if people could test it on other platforms

Added new mod_jk README describing simplified build/install process, including new build-unix.sh and install-unix.sh scripts.  Please read through this and see if it works when you test the build/install.
Note that we need to document build process on Windows; if you feel like it, do so inside README
